==English==
===Etymology===
[[Category:Greek derivations]]
From [[Ancient Greek]] '''[[πάνθηρ]]''' (''panther'') "total hunter", from '''[[πάν]]''' (''pan'') "total" + '''[[θήρα]]''' (''thera'') "hunting".

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun-reg}}

#Any of various [[big cat]]s with black fur.
#Any big cat of the genus ''[[Panthera]]''.

